            <thetext>This is a reminder bug for the native Undo/Redo in Safari / Windows.

The native execCommands &quot;undo&quot; and &quot;redo&quot; do not work correctly in Safari / Windows. 

The issues are the following:

  * redo does not work reliable
  * user *can* end up with broken content when using undo / redo
  * content is selected after the commands undo / redo
  
There is a related bug report open ( https://bugs.webkit.org/show_bug.cgi?id=6692 ) which describes that the Undo stack is not bulletproof.</thetext>
          </long_desc>
